reviewText:
The two movies are pretty decent. A Cinderella Story is a bit bland, while Another Cinderella Story is a bit more lively and humorous.
FYI to let those interested in purchasing this product is that the disk only contains the two movies and nothing else. They do not contain special features of any kind.
Great Hi School angst movies.
I was so happy with this purchase and the product was so great, I am very happy and would recommend this seller to everybody! I will be back to buy from this seller for sure! Thank you so much!
fun
Love it
my daughter knew about one of the stories and she enjoyed both of them so it was a good value for us.
It is so nice to be able to watch a good clean entertaining movie, there are to few out there to watch.  I would recommend this to every one.
The movie is advertise and sold as a double feature, but I only got one movie (A Cinderella Story) Another Cinderella Story is missing
Lots of fund and good clean humor. Nice life lessons in both stories. Liked the music and dance in Another Cinderella Story. My 4 year old girl really liked it.
My daughters loved this movie the first time they saw it on tv. They kept asking to see it again. I found it here for a great price.
this was a great movie to watch when it is raining and want to watch it with the girls. yeah
Great movie for young girls. Great deal: you get 2 movies for the price of one. You can't beat that.
My daughter loves it and so do I.  Recommend.......to all ages.  You will not regret it. So much fun to watch with kids.
Saturday night teenage sleepover hit! Works every time, no matter how many times these movies are seen.  Even the adults in your family will enjoy these!
my daughter loves these movies and now she can watch them any time instead of waiting for them to be on tv
Got here fast and secure. It was in great shape and works perfectly fine in my dvd player. Thank you so much.

This was a birthday gift for our daughter who turned 9.  She already saw these movies on the Family Channel and loved them as I did too.  This was what she wanted for her birthday and was very happy to get both movies for a great price.
I have no clue why I love these movies; but I do, and to get them both, in a set, for less than $10 was amazing!  It arrived quickly, also!

Daughter, 9 loves the original story with Hillary Duff. This is a repurchase after her original was damaged.
 Rating based on a 9 year old's opinion, not mine as a  grown up.
It was a good DVD. It has one side with Cinderella Story, and the other side with Another Cinderella Story. Both stories are good.
Great combination of movies!
make sure to flip the disk to watch the other movie
Great packaging and arrived in a great box not broken
Perfect condition, got here in 2 days. I love this movie and was a good buy.

Only received a Cinderella Story when it says it's both. I checked if the one DVD had both movies on it and still only appeared to have one on the disk. Very Disappointed!!
